1
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:29,660
♪In the stormy night♪

2
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:37,340
♪The dark hair of a charming woman
is reflected in the flame of a candle♪

3
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:41,300
♪Shrouded by year
after year of memories♪

4
00:00:41,980 --> 00:00:45,780
♪I can do nothing but feign indifference♪

5
00:00:46,220 --> 00:00:53,140
♪Outlining your cheeks♪

6
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:55,540
♪Together and apart,
just like quicksand♪

7
00:00:55,740 --> 00:00:57,420
♪I'm meant to make peace with myself♪

8
00:00:57,660 --> 00:01:01,140
♪Rebuild or crumble♪

9
00:01:01,420 --> 00:01:03,780
♪Drift away in the clouds♪

10
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:05,660
♪Driving away♪

11
00:01:06,020 --> 00:01:09,300
♪Your dashing pretense♪

12
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:11,620
♪A drunken dream♪

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:13,500
♪A person I miss♪

14
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:16,860
♪Of course I know if it's real♪

15
00:01:17,060 --> 00:01:21,660
♪Even if you're just by my side♪

16
00:01:22,180 --> 00:01:28,220
♪I want to hold on to you
but I can only play dumb♪

17
00:01:29,940 --> 00:01:35,060
[In Blossom]

18
00:01:36,060 --> 00:01:38,740
[Episode 5]

19
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,120
Mr. Pan.

20
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,590
Why are you taking me here?

21
00:01:53,190 --> 00:01:54,480
Do you still want to pretend?

22
00:01:56,550 --> 00:01:57,400
What do you mean?

23
00:01:57,590 --> 00:01:58,310
I don't know.

24
00:01:59,310 --> 00:02:02,270
Does this place seem familiar to you?

25
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:06,870
The carriage passed through here

26
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:08,550
before going to Sunrise Garden.

27
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:09,830
Why is that so?

28
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:16,000
I fell sick and can't remember anything.

29
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:18,390
Don't play dumb with me.

30
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:21,080
I want the truth.

31
00:02:22,030 --> 00:02:23,600
I have been telling the truth.

32
00:02:23,670 --> 00:02:24,830
But you never trusted me.

33
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:27,390
Fine, let's say you can't remember.

34
00:02:27,910 --> 00:02:29,000
Let me refresh your memory.

35
00:02:29,470 --> 00:02:30,830
Did you abduct Yang Caiwei

36
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:32,030
from the Coffin House

37
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:33,550
and bring her here

38
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:35,110
to kill her?

39
00:02:36,830 --> 00:02:38,320
Turns out he only knows

40
00:02:38,470 --> 00:02:40,110
that Shangguan Zhi abducted me.

41
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,030
He didn't suspect my identity.

42
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:43,270
Yes.

43
00:02:44,110 --> 00:02:44,830
I admit

44
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:47,720
that I abducted Miss Yang
in the heat of the moment.

45
00:02:48,270 --> 00:02:50,030
But she ran off and married you.

46
00:02:51,110 --> 00:02:52,880
Do you want
to settle the scores with me now?

47
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:55,270
Yes, she did run away.

48
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:56,960
So you followed her to Sunrise Garden,

49
00:02:57,030 --> 00:02:59,160
sneaked into the pleasure house

50
00:02:59,390 --> 00:03:00,630
and pushed her down.

51
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,750
I didn't.

52
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:03,800
How do you explain this, then?

53
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,880
I found it on Yang Caiwei's body.

54
00:03:10,110 --> 00:03:12,190
Does it jog your memory, Miss Shangguan?

55
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:15,030
Since Shangguan Zhi

56
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,600
intended to use my identity,

57
00:03:17,030 --> 00:03:18,550
why did she keep this?

58
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,470
You liquored me up

59
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,520
to read the case file,

60
00:03:23,830 --> 00:03:25,520
because you are scared
that you might have left something

61
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,390
at the crime scene, right?

62
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:31,320
I was only concerned
about Miss Yang's case.

63
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,080
Shangguan Zhi.

64
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,880
Tell me the truth,

65
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:38,470
or you are not leaving here alive.

66
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,440
Pan Yue.

67
00:03:47,670 --> 00:03:48,720
What exactly do you want?

68
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,670
Pay blood for blood.

69
00:04:01,160 --> 00:04:01,720
Fine.

70
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,520
Are you insane?

71
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:09,630
Didn't you say you want to take my life?

72
00:04:15,110 --> 00:04:16,230
I know

73
00:04:18,510 --> 00:04:19,760
you are suspecting me,

74
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:21,440
and I can't prove myself.

75
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:24,920
Look at this.

76
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,760
These are my henchmen.

77
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,270
Before heading to the Coffin House,

78
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:04,040
I had planned

79
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:06,040
to leave Miss Yang alone

80
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,670
in this abandoned mine pit.

81
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:09,070
I was trying to scare her off

82
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:11,640
from approaching you.

83
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:12,950
Unexpectedly,

84
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,200
a bunch of bandits followed us

85
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:15,390
and snatched our things.

86
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,550
They even pushed us into the pit.

87
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:19,000
Fortunately,

88
00:05:19,230 --> 00:05:20,110
branches were preventing us

89
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:20,880
from falling to our deaths.

90
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,480
Then, we climbed out of the pit.

91
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,230
I asked her
to drive the carriage and leave.

92
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,480
I collapsed halfway

93
00:05:26,550 --> 00:05:27,270
from exhaustion.

94
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,200
I doubt you would be so kind.

95
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:33,040
I thought you two hadn't met
each other for ten years

96
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,040
and had grown apart.

97
00:05:34,790 --> 00:05:37,230
But after hearing what she said,

98
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,880
I realized that the bond between you two
runs so deeply.

99
00:05:46,790 --> 00:05:47,720
Which makes my one-sided affection

100
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:50,790
seem rather insignificant.

101
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,390
I know I couldn't change anything.

102
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:54,950
So

103
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,200
I decided to let go of my obsession

104
00:05:57,350 --> 00:05:58,550
and gave her the marriage fortune stick.

105
00:05:59,070 --> 00:06:00,640
I wish you both be happy together.

106
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:05,270
What did she tell you?

107
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,000
She said

108
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:13,110
when the Yang family ran into problems,
she went to you

109
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,040
but was shut out.

110
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:16,790
Then, she ended up living
on the streets in Heyang.

111
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:20,000
Besides, she was insulted and mocked
because of the scar on her face.

112
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:21,880
She began to believe

113
00:06:22,110 --> 00:06:23,480
that dead people are more reliable
than the living.

114
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,040
She used to think

115
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:27,270
that you both had already grown apart.

116
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,720
But she didn't expect you
to come to Heyang for her

117
00:06:30,790 --> 00:06:31,790
after ten years.

118
00:06:32,790 --> 00:06:34,550
Turns out
it was just a misunderstanding.

119
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,320
She believed you

120
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:38,320
and truly wanted

121
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:41,320
to marry you.

122
00:06:43,900 --> 00:06:47,580
♪I can do nothing but feign indifference♪

123
00:06:48,620 --> 00:06:55,860
♪Outlining your cheeks♪

124
00:06:56,340 --> 00:06:58,340
♪Together and apart,
just like quicksand♪

125
00:06:58,510 --> 00:06:59,790
You told her

126
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:01,920
she is the only woman
you want to marry in this lifetime

127
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,830
no matter what.

128
00:07:05,350 --> 00:07:06,600
Be it ten years ago...

129
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,350
Or ten years later,

130
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:13,270
you are the only woman
I want to marry in this lifetime.

131
00:07:14,300 --> 00:07:19,820
♪A person I miss.
Of course I know if it's real♪

132
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:24,070
The coachman will take you back.

133
00:07:24,340 --> 00:07:30,860
♪I want to hold on to you
but I can only play dumb♪

134
00:07:39,830 --> 00:07:43,140
[Heyang's Soup and Flatbread,
Flatbread, Tea]

135
00:07:43,140 --> 00:07:46,340
[Chunlai Inn, Wanshun Grocery]

136
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:04,550
Bao.

137
00:08:04,670 --> 00:08:05,760
Young Master Zhuo
of Silver Rain Terrace is here.

138
00:08:05,830 --> 00:08:06,390
We should go now.

139
00:08:07,270 --> 00:08:08,510
Come here and let me have a look.

140
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:17,440
Young Master wants you there.

141
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,670
Why are you afraid of me?

142
00:08:32,790 --> 00:08:36,790
People said the young master
of Silver Rain Terrace eats people.

143
00:08:41,470 --> 00:08:42,960
Come closer and let me

144
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,670
have a taste of you.

145
00:08:44,670 --> 00:08:45,590
Please spare us.

146
00:08:47,550 --> 00:08:48,440
What a killjoy.

147
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:04,230
While you were away for the past month,

148
00:09:04,470 --> 00:09:06,520
Heyang has changed tremendously.

149
00:09:07,590 --> 00:09:08,470
I know.

150
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:12,840
Pan Yue is on bad terms
with the other three clans.

151
00:09:13,790 --> 00:09:15,790
Pan Yue demands 400,000 taels of silver

152
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:18,000
because he intends
to make it hard on us.

153
00:09:18,110 --> 00:09:19,280
Mr. Cai and the rest

154
00:09:19,590 --> 00:09:21,400
are going to do something to Pan Yue.

155
00:09:22,350 --> 00:09:23,710
Get physical again?

156
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,280
This is not fun at all.

157
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:27,280
Inform the other three clans

158
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:30,280
that Pan Yue is ours now.

159
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,470
I'm going to destroy him

160
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,520
and chuck him out of Heyang.

161
00:09:46,470 --> 00:09:47,000
Caiwei.

162
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:48,910
Careful.

163
00:09:50,150 --> 00:09:50,760
He is inside.

164
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:51,880
All right.

165
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:55,670
Give me the money first.

166
00:09:58,760 --> 00:09:59,440
Let's go.

167
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:22,320
Master.

168
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:24,470
It is me.

169
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:29,840
You...

170
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,470
If middle fingers are pinched, victims
die in the hours of Zi, Wu, Mao, or You.

171
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:38,200
If the hands are open, they die
in the hours of Chen, Xu, Chou, or Mo.

172
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,840
If the fists are clenched, they die
in the hours of Yin, Shen, Si, or Hai.

173
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:44,640
This is how you determine
the time of death.

174
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:48,840
Caiwei.

175
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:53,200
Master.

176
00:10:54,110 --> 00:10:56,590
I thought I would never see you again.

177
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,590
Caiwei.

178
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,590
Caiwei, you...

179
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:05,230
Your face has changed.

180
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:08,840
How do you feel?

181
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:13,910
I'm not used to it yet.

182
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,760
I don't dare to put a mirror
beside my bed.

183
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:19,320
I'm afraid I will scare myself
if I wake up at midnight.

184
00:11:20,150 --> 00:11:21,960
When I see my face with blood all over,

185
00:11:22,230 --> 00:11:23,080
I think

186
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,320
that it's not Shangguan Zhi who died

187
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:26,710
but me.

188
00:11:28,550 --> 00:11:29,200
Caiwei.

189
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:31,840
It has been a tough time for you.

190
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:34,000
It's nothing for me.

191
00:11:34,350 --> 00:11:35,840
I'm just worried
that I might get you involved.

192
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:42,350
Master.

193
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:44,030
Where have you been for the past month?

194
00:11:44,590 --> 00:11:46,030
What has happened to the Coffin House?

195
00:11:47,030 --> 00:11:48,470
On the night of your wedding,

196
00:11:48,710 --> 00:11:50,520
a masked man tried to kill me.

197
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:51,470
Luckily,

198
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:52,840
I took the medicine

199
00:11:53,030 --> 00:11:54,320
and regained consciousness.

200
00:11:54,550 --> 00:11:55,640
I managed to escape
from the Coffin House

201
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:57,200
before he noticed me.

202
00:11:57,470 --> 00:11:59,440
Did you see his face?

203
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:03,030
I couldn't.

204
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:04,110
But

205
00:12:04,550 --> 00:12:06,960
that person was wearing
the groom's gown.

206
00:12:10,590 --> 00:12:12,110
Pan Yue is indeed cruel.

207
00:12:12,590 --> 00:12:13,640
He wanted to kill you.

208
00:12:15,150 --> 00:12:15,790
Caiwei.

209
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,640
Are you safe

210
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:19,000
with him?

211
00:12:20,110 --> 00:12:21,200
He did suspect me.

212
00:12:21,670 --> 00:12:23,880
But I'm safe for the time being.

213
00:12:24,110 --> 00:12:25,400
So I can focus on investigating him now.

214
00:12:25,670 --> 00:12:26,280
Good.

215
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,230
What is your plan?

216
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:30,880
I need to find Shangguan Zhi's body

217
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,280
and examine it.

218
00:12:32,670 --> 00:12:34,350
Perhaps I might find evidence
against him.

219
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:37,670
All right.

220
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:39,710
You ought to be careful.

221
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:42,110
Keep yourself safe no matter what.

222
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:42,840
Understand?

223
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,000
Yes.

224
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,320
You also need to be careful.

225
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:46,760
Don't leave the city if possible.

226
00:12:46,880 --> 00:12:47,840
Just stay here to recuperate.

227
00:12:48,470 --> 00:12:49,960
I will. Don't worry about me.

228
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:51,470
Oh, right.

229
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:03,910
Thank you, Master.

230
00:13:18,710 --> 00:13:19,350
Stop the carriage.

231
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:33,670
Go and check on the horse harness.

232
00:13:33,670 --> 00:13:34,080
Yes.

233
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:05,710
I must reclaim my identity
as Yang Caiwei as soon as possible.

234
00:14:09,980 --> 00:14:12,460
[Edify through music and ritual]

235
00:14:22,670 --> 00:14:23,440
Mr. Pan.

236
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,790
Do you think Miss Shangguan will come

237
00:14:25,880 --> 00:14:27,280
after you wronged her yesterday?

238
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:29,230
Did I ask that?

239
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:53,880
Ling.

240
00:14:54,400 --> 00:14:57,080
Is Miss Shangguan moving out of here?

241
00:14:57,470 --> 00:14:58,320
Of course not.

242
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:02,280
I'm here to serve the people.

243
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,280
How could I withdraw

244
00:15:03,350 --> 00:15:04,550
before I contribute anything?

245
00:15:06,350 --> 00:15:07,150
It's just

246
00:15:07,230 --> 00:15:08,470
that I want to keep my distance
from Mr. Pan

247
00:15:08,590 --> 00:15:09,710
so as not to annoy him.

248
00:15:19,670 --> 00:15:20,320
Shangguan Zhi.

249
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:21,520
Yes.

250
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:23,230
Copy this scroll.

251
00:15:25,400 --> 00:15:26,110
Yes.

252
00:15:26,460 --> 00:15:27,100
[Hunter Qiao Chong Case]

253
00:15:41,790 --> 00:15:42,350
Mr. Pan.

254
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:44,640
Mr. Pan!

255
00:15:44,790 --> 00:15:46,320
This is bad! Someone reports a case.

256
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,470
Liu.

257
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:49,210
This is the county yamen.

258
00:15:49,210 --> 00:15:50,960
Do you expect people to come for tea
instead of reporting a case?

259
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:51,880
But...

260
00:15:52,150 --> 00:15:53,400
But the one reporting is

261
00:15:53,880 --> 00:15:55,150
from Silver Rain Terrace.

262
00:15:56,060 --> 00:16:00,140
[Heyang Magistrate's Office]

263
00:16:05,110 --> 00:16:06,790
Isn't he the head of Silver Rain Terrace?

264
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,030
Let's go and check it out.

265
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:09,000
What is he doing in the county yamen?

266
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:10,790
Come on. Let's go.

267
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:12,150
Let's have a look.

268
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:13,320
Why does he come here?

269
00:16:13,400 --> 00:16:14,150
This is the county yamen.

270
00:16:14,150 --> 00:16:15,080
Hurry on.

271
00:16:15,520 --> 00:16:16,320
Let's check it out.

272
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:17,640
[Court]
What does Silver Rain Terrace want to do?

273
00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:18,470
It is terrifying.

274
00:16:18,710 --> 00:16:20,350
Let me see. Make way.

275
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:21,280
Move aside.

276
00:16:29,670 --> 00:16:30,840
I, Sun Zhen,

277
00:16:31,670 --> 00:16:33,520
would like to report a case
on behalf of my young master.

278
00:16:34,670 --> 00:16:36,790
Who are you reporting,
and what is it for?

279
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:39,470
Pan Yue killed his own wife.

280
