A month ago,

285
00:16:55,520 --> 00:16:57,590
Mr. Pan forced a commoner,
Yang Caiwei, to marry him.

286
00:16:57,790 --> 00:16:58,520
Miss Yang

287
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:01,110
fell off the building
on her wedding night.

288
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:03,470
This case is hastily closed as suicide.

289
00:17:04,310 --> 00:17:06,160
While Miss Yang was working
at the Coffin House,

290
00:17:06,190 --> 00:17:07,590
she had already been mistreated
over the years.

291
00:17:07,680 --> 00:17:08,710
If she had wanted to kill herself,

292
00:17:09,430 --> 00:17:10,920
she would have died a hundred times.

293
00:17:11,880 --> 00:17:15,190
But why did she choose to jump
off the building on her wedding day?

294
00:17:16,350 --> 00:17:17,590
My young master feels sorry

295
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:20,230
for Miss Yang's unclear death.

296
00:17:20,430 --> 00:17:21,640
Today, we would like

297
00:17:22,590 --> 00:17:24,070
to seek justice for her.

298
00:17:24,710 --> 00:17:25,950
That makes sense.

299
00:17:26,470 --> 00:17:28,590
The ugly woman doesn't seem like one
who would take her own life.

300
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:30,040
Could it be real?

301
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:30,950
Nonsense.

302
00:17:31,110 --> 00:17:32,520
Mr. Pan isn't that kind of person.

303
00:17:32,760 --> 00:17:33,830
You never know.

304
00:17:34,230 --> 00:17:36,470
It seems that Silver Rain Terrace
uses this incident

305
00:17:36,760 --> 00:17:38,230
to make things difficult for Pan Yue.

306
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:42,520
Why don't I make good use
of this chance?

307
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:46,560
Even if Miss Yang's death is suspicious,

308
00:17:47,070 --> 00:17:49,640
how can you prove
that the murderer is Mr. Pan?

309
00:17:50,280 --> 00:17:51,430
Do you have any evidence?

310
00:17:51,830 --> 00:17:53,640
That's the yamen's job.

311
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,470
Mr. Pan, your appeal to the people

312
00:17:55,470 --> 00:17:57,560
sounds resolute.

313
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:59,230
But after the incident that day,

314
00:17:59,760 --> 00:18:01,880
you abused the right as a censor

315
00:18:02,430 --> 00:18:04,680
to hinder the investigation
of the former county magistrate.

316
00:18:05,190 --> 00:18:06,280
After being impeached,

317
00:18:06,710 --> 00:18:08,110
you returned to Heyang

318
00:18:08,190 --> 00:18:10,160
as the county magistrate.

319
00:18:10,800 --> 00:18:11,950
Mr. Pan,

320
00:18:12,040 --> 00:18:13,640
do you think

321
00:18:13,760 --> 00:18:16,680
you could hush everyone
in Heyang up by doing so?

322
00:18:17,190 --> 00:18:20,310
How could a murderer
who trampled on the laws

323
00:18:20,760 --> 00:18:23,070
become the rightful official

324
00:18:23,280 --> 00:18:25,350
of Heyang?

325
00:18:25,520 --> 00:18:27,680
Pan Yue killed his wife.
This is outrageous!

326
