This is outrageous!

330
00:18:39,710 --> 00:18:41,470
I haven't met
with your young master before.

331
00:18:42,110 --> 00:18:45,040
But I'm genuinely impressed
by his kind resolution.

332
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:48,280
Although the falling-off-building case
has been closed,

333
00:18:49,040 --> 00:18:50,880
if someone questions it,

334
00:18:51,040 --> 00:18:53,520
I will re-examine the case

335
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:56,640
and give you a satisfactory answer.

336
00:18:57,230 --> 00:18:59,880
My young master isn't patient.

337
00:19:00,640 --> 00:19:02,000
In seven days,

338
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:04,640
you must give the people
of Heyang an answer.

339
00:19:05,230 --> 00:19:08,040
What do you say, Mr. Pan?

340
00:19:10,310 --> 00:19:12,160
Heyang is under the protection
of Silver Rain Terrace.

341
00:19:12,590 --> 00:19:14,800
Since you are speaking
on behalf of Silver Rain Terrace,

342
00:19:15,110 --> 00:19:16,760
how could I defy you?

343
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:19,830
I will wait for your answer.

344
00:19:29,040 --> 00:19:30,760
He even comes to the yamen.

345
00:19:31,310 --> 00:19:32,310
Let's go.

346
00:19:34,710 --> 00:19:35,350
Liu.

347
00:19:35,520 --> 00:19:36,950
The court is adjourned.

348
00:19:37,040 --> 00:19:38,110
Why are your legs trembling?

349
00:19:38,190 --> 00:19:40,350
San, let me tell you this.

350
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:42,640
Judging what happened today,

351
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:46,070
Silver Rain Terrace
won't let it slide easily.

352
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:49,160
I bet they are going to torture us.

353
00:19:51,950 --> 00:19:52,520
Liu.

354
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:54,520
Both sides are no one to mess with.

355
00:19:54,710 --> 00:19:57,160
We are very likely
to be caught in the crossfire.

356
00:19:58,470 --> 00:19:59,710
In the worst-case scenario,

357
00:20:00,070 --> 00:20:01,760
we would be better off leaving here.

358
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:04,190
That's all we can do.

359
00:20:14,310 --> 00:20:14,920
Young Master.

360
00:20:15,590 --> 00:20:16,760
Pan Yue took the case.

361
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:23,160
He has some nerve.

362
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:26,000
I would like to see

363
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:28,430
how he will clean up after himself.

364
00:20:36,040 --> 00:20:38,920
Pan Yue promised
to reveal the truth in seven days,

365
00:20:39,640 --> 00:20:41,950
but he can't possibly turn himself in.

366
00:20:42,830 --> 00:20:44,430
What plan is he hatching?

367
00:20:46,110 --> 00:20:48,160
Silver Rain Terrace
has been imperious lately.

368
00:20:48,560 --> 00:20:50,190
Have you come up with a plan

369
00:20:50,280 --> 00:20:51,350
to deal with them?

370
00:20:52,040 --> 00:20:53,430
What do you think?

371
00:20:55,190 --> 00:20:56,640
Should we

372
00:20:57,190 --> 00:20:59,230
examine Miss Yang's body publicly?

373
00:21:05,230 --> 00:21:07,110
I... I'm not sure about this.

374
00:21:07,470 --> 00:21:08,880
But they claimed

375
00:21:08,950 --> 00:21:10,110
that you impeded the investigation.

376
00:21:10,430 --> 00:21:12,230
Why don't you examine the body publicly

377
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:14,830
to show that you aren't

378
00:21:14,920 --> 00:21:15,760
hiding anything?

379
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,760
And the rumors would stop.

380
00:21:18,830 --> 00:21:20,230
I never cared about the rumors.

381
00:21:20,470 --> 00:21:21,920
Why are you concerned about it?

382
00:21:24,310 --> 00:21:25,230
I will do it.

383
00:21:25,310 --> 00:21:25,920
Allow me.

384
00:21:26,560 --> 00:21:28,800
I'm thinking, if Miss Yang knows

385
00:21:28,830 --> 00:21:30,800
that you are wronged because of her,

386
00:21:30,920 --> 00:21:32,190
she wouldn't rest in peace.

387
00:21:33,350 --> 00:21:35,160
Before I put you in prison,

388
00:21:35,280 --> 00:21:36,560
I won't be at ease.

389
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:39,190
It seems that you pay extra attention
to her case.

390
00:21:43,430 --> 00:21:44,760
Because

391
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:46,230
we have known each other
since childhood.

392
00:21:46,590 --> 00:21:47,710
Besides, you suspect me.

393
00:21:48,190 --> 00:21:50,190
So I'm thinking of proving my innocence.

394
00:21:50,280 --> 00:21:51,310
There is nothing to investigate.

395
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:53,230
She died in an accident.

396
00:21:55,310 --> 00:21:56,400
But seven days later...

397
00:21:56,430 --> 00:21:57,640
I have a plan.

398
00:21:58,190 --> 00:21:59,280
What plan?

399
00:22:01,280 --> 00:22:02,000
Do you want to know?

400
00:22:10,950 --> 00:22:12,830
But I don't want to tell you.

401
00:22:32,950 --> 00:22:34,680
He seems confident.

402
00:22:35,070 --> 00:22:37,680
I shall see what is up your sleeve.

403
00:22:41,610 --> 00:22:42,760
Mr. Pan, here's your letter.

404
00:23:19,140 --> 00:23:21,100
[Mr. Pan, please...]

405
00:23:23,040 --> 00:23:24,190
Hundred Flowers Court?

406
00:23:26,980 --> 00:23:29,740
[Hundred Flowers Court]

407
00:23:41,710 --> 00:23:43,280
Mr. Li, let me pour for you.

408
00:23:43,280 --> 00:23:44,190
Come on.

409
00:23:44,430 --> 00:23:44,880
Here.

410
00:23:45,230 --> 00:23:46,160
One more.

411
00:23:58,680 --> 00:24:00,280
Sir, do you want some?

412
00:24:01,000 --> 00:24:01,560
Sure.

413
00:24:03,070 --> 00:24:03,560
Come.

414
00:24:04,110 --> 00:24:04,560
Please drink.

415
00:24:06,590 --> 00:24:07,310
Young lady, come over here.

416
00:24:07,310 --> 00:24:07,880
Sure.

417
00:24:10,230 --> 00:24:11,800
Coming.

418
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:15,470
Come hither, beauty.

419
00:24:16,110 --> 00:24:17,110
Don't go.

420
00:24:22,680 --> 00:24:24,190
Naughty.

421
00:24:28,680 --> 00:24:30,160
Sir, come and get me.

422
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,310
Don't go.

423
00:24:33,710 --> 00:24:36,230
Come. Have a drink with me.

424
00:24:36,230 --> 00:24:36,590
Cheers.

425
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:52,430
We have an important guest
in the private room.

426
00:24:52,470 --> 00:24:53,310
Hurry over.

427
00:24:53,430 --> 00:24:53,800
Sure.

428
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:55,950
Come with me.

429
00:24:56,070 --> 00:24:57,400
Coming.

430
00:24:58,590 --> 00:24:59,040
Quick.

431
00:25:02,520 --> 00:25:03,160
Hurry.

432
00:25:05,430 --> 00:25:06,040
Hurry up.

433
00:25:06,160 --> 00:25:07,430
Come on.

434
00:25:07,800 --> 00:25:09,470
I wonder if I will be chosen.

435
00:25:10,190 --> 00:25:11,040
I want to be chosen.

436
00:25:11,070 --> 00:25:12,830
I have prepared a good tune.

437
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:15,160
They will definitely choose me.

438
00:25:16,880 --> 00:25:18,350
- Let's go.
- It is our turn.

439
00:25:18,430 --> 00:25:19,190
Come on.

440
00:26:14,590 --> 00:26:16,310
Sorry to keep you waiting, Mr. Pan.

441
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:17,590
Please pardon me.

442
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:21,920
I'm willing to wait for the beauties.

443
00:26:23,040 --> 00:26:25,000
I won't blame you, Miss Qing.

444
00:26:37,110 --> 00:26:39,590
That explains why all ladies

445
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:41,190
fall for you.

446
00:26:41,680 --> 00:26:45,920
You are indeed handsome
and good-natured.

447
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:52,800
However,

448
00:26:53,070 --> 00:26:55,640
the young master
of Silver Rain Terrace is targeting you.

449
00:26:56,110 --> 00:26:58,710
You will probably

450
00:26:59,040 --> 00:27:00,640
have a hard time in Heyang.

451
00:27:05,760 --> 00:27:08,830
Is the young master
someone hard to deal with?

452
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:09,800
Zhuo Lanjiang

453
00:27:10,280 --> 00:27:11,760
is the only son of Zhuo Shanju.

454
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:13,880
He had been studying in the capital.

455
00:27:14,590 --> 00:27:15,830
Three years ago,

456
00:27:16,470 --> 00:27:18,070
a new power arrived in Heyang,

457
00:27:18,190 --> 00:27:19,470
Gold Water Sect.

458
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:21,350
They were ferocious

459
00:27:21,680 --> 00:27:23,800
and competed
with Silver Rain Terrace for business.

460
00:27:24,230 --> 00:27:27,000
Mr. Zhuo lost his life
in the competition.

461
00:27:27,430 --> 00:27:29,680
The young Zhuo Lanjiang
then rushed back.

462
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:31,880
No one knows

463
00:27:32,000 --> 00:27:35,000
what happened that night.

464
00:27:37,070 --> 00:27:39,040
People found
that the river turned all red

465
00:27:39,400 --> 00:27:42,310
when they woke up in the morning.

466
00:27:42,560 --> 00:27:44,680
The heads of the Gold Water Sect members

467
00:27:44,920 --> 00:27:47,190
were hanging on the city gate.

468
00:27:48,230 --> 00:27:49,800
I heard that Silver Rain Terrace

469
00:27:49,880 --> 00:27:51,710
wiped out this sect three years ago.

470
00:27:52,230 --> 00:27:55,160
I didn't expect it to be his doing.

471
00:27:59,950 --> 00:28:01,800
Miss Qing, you invited me over

472
00:28:02,430 --> 00:28:05,590
to praise Silver Rain Terrace
in front of me?

473
00:28:07,310 --> 00:28:08,400
Of course not.

474
00:28:15,920 --> 00:28:18,310
Mr. Pan, you are dashing,

475
00:28:18,920 --> 00:28:21,110
and I'm attracted to you at first sight.

476
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:24,710
I'm meeting you late at night

477
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:27,560
because I want to do something

478
00:28:27,590 --> 00:28:31,310
those women wish for but dare not do.

479
00:28:36,280 --> 00:28:40,040
Despite being a woman,

480
00:28:40,800 --> 00:28:43,680
the Hundred Flowers Court has earned
its place among the Four Greats.

481
00:28:44,040 --> 00:28:47,040
You are exceptionally powerful to me.

482
00:28:48,070 --> 00:28:51,830
If I believe in such jests,

483
00:28:52,040 --> 00:28:55,190
I would be underestimating you.

484
00:28:57,230 --> 00:28:58,000
Anyway,

485
00:28:58,680 --> 00:29:00,190
since I have come here
at your invitation,

486
00:29:01,110 --> 00:29:02,710
to show my respect,

487
00:29:03,710 --> 00:29:05,040
I will drink first.

488
00:29:19,350 --> 00:29:19,800
All right.

489
00:29:22,070 --> 00:29:24,560
Mr. Pan, you are straightforward.

490
00:29:25,280 --> 00:29:27,230
I will cut right to the chase.

491
00:29:27,950 --> 00:29:29,640
You will probably expect
a fight with the Four Greats

492
00:29:29,760 --> 00:29:31,680
since you came to Heyang.

493
00:29:32,520 --> 00:29:35,400
The Hundred Flowers Court
would like to be your ally

494
00:29:35,640 --> 00:29:38,000
and assist you.

495
00:29:40,280 --> 00:29:43,470
How do you know there will be a fight?

496
00:29:43,800 --> 00:29:44,400
If not,

497
00:29:44,800 --> 00:29:46,950
your effort coming to Heyang

498
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:48,800
would be in vain.

499
00:29:50,560 --> 00:29:52,070
If you want to achieve something big,

500
00:29:52,280 --> 00:29:54,430
taking down the Four Greats

501
00:29:54,560 --> 00:29:55,950
could help you gain a big reputation.

502
00:29:57,880 --> 00:29:58,920
It sounds reasonable.

503
00:29:59,950 --> 00:30:02,470
However, the Four Greats
are thick as thieves.

504
00:30:03,310 --> 00:30:04,640
How do I know

505
00:30:05,560 --> 00:30:09,310
if this isn't a honeytrap
from the Hundred Flowers Court?

506
00:30:14,040 --> 00:30:15,590
Among the Four Greats,

507
00:30:15,590 --> 00:30:17,560
I'm not convinced to rank the last.

508
00:30:18,830 --> 00:30:21,950
Silver Rain Terrace is domineering
over everything,

509
00:30:23,280 --> 00:30:26,590
while Gu Yong of Relief Hall is greedy.

510
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:28,400
As long as you pay him enough money,

511
00:30:28,470 --> 00:30:31,640
he wouldn't hesitate

512
00:30:31,710 --> 00:30:33,560
to stab his own father.

513
00:30:34,680 --> 00:30:35,400
Also,

514
00:30:35,430 --> 00:30:38,920
Cai Sheng of Life and Death House
is a reckless man.

515
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:40,310
He is foolhardy.

516
00:30:41,590 --> 00:30:42,280
If you are down

517
00:30:42,520 --> 00:30:43,590
for this fight,

518
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:46,070
I will assist you

519
00:30:46,070 --> 00:30:47,800
and triumph over
the rest of the Four Greats.

520
00:30:49,470 --> 00:30:52,590
Do you think I will win?

521
00:30:56,280 --> 00:30:58,040
I always have a good assessment

522
00:30:59,040 --> 00:31:00,680
of men.

523
00:31:02,230 --> 00:31:04,950
All right. I promise you.

524
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:11,000
These two actually gang up.

525
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:13,280
But words alone aren't enough.

526
00:31:13,830 --> 00:31:17,280
Should you show some sincerity,
Miss Qing?

527
00:31:19,560 --> 00:31:20,800
Don't worry, Mr. Pan.

528
00:31:21,070 --> 00:31:24,590
I have prepared a gift for you.

529
00:31:30,800 --> 00:31:31,430
Here.

530
00:31:31,760 --> 00:31:34,830
May everything go smoothly for you
in Heyang

531
00:31:35,040 --> 00:31:36,430
and may you get promoted.

532
00:31:36,710 --> 00:31:41,190
May the Hundred Flowers Court
shine its radiance upon Heyang.

533
00:31:47,470 --> 00:31:48,310
Change the tune.

534
00:31:49,040 --> 00:31:50,040
Yes.

535
00:32:17,430 --> 00:32:18,680
You have ruined Mr. Pan's mood.

536
00:32:18,760 --> 00:32:19,920
Go down and receive your punishment.

537
00:32:20,950 --> 00:32:21,560
Yes.

538
00:32:21,560 --> 00:32:22,230
Hold on.

539
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:29,800
Did you play the wrong note on purpose?

540
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:35,590
It seems that you are interested in me.

541
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:39,160
Come with me tonight.

542
00:32:43,880 --> 00:32:44,950
I bid you farewell, Mr. Pan.

543
00:32:47,430 --> 00:32:48,110
I shall take my leave.

544
00:32:59,350 --> 00:32:59,830
Miss Qing.

545
00:33:00,430 --> 00:33:02,000
Is he the one you chose?

546
00:33:03,800 --> 00:33:04,760
I will take this chance.

547
00:33:05,800 --> 00:33:07,880
Perhaps he could help me

548
00:33:08,520 --> 00:33:10,310
to achieve my wish.

549
00:33:22,310 --> 00:33:23,760
Didn't you want
to keep your distance from me?

550
00:33:24,190 --> 00:33:25,190
Why did you follow me there?

551
00:33:27,520 --> 00:33:30,400
You surely have a way
to take your enemies down.

552
00:33:30,760 --> 00:33:32,230
You joined hands
with one of the Four Greats.

553
00:33:32,310 --> 00:33:33,310
This is impressive.

554
00:33:33,590 --> 00:33:35,800
It seems that Heyang will soon...

555
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:36,640
Stop flattering me.

556
00:33:42,230 --> 00:33:43,560
Please don't take me wrong.

557
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:45,830
I thought you were investigating
the falling-off-building case.

